      • pots and pans organizer
      • Measure Your Cabinet SpaceBefore purchasing, please measure the size of your cabinet space to ensure a perfect fit. Because our pot rack takes up a certain amount of space after storing pots and pans, if it is too large, you will not be able to use it. Please make sure your cabinet is within the recommended size range (Min width 24in; Min Height 18.5in; Min Depth 9in).
      • Only 2 Minutes to InstallStore your pots & pans three different ways with this pots and pans organizer. You can stack them vertically on both sides or just one side or even horizontally for tighter spaces. Its very simple to put together, no tools needed.
      • Upgraded & Enhanced StabilityThe M-shaped groove is made deeper so that the MUDEELA pots and pans organizer fits most pots and lids commonly used at home. Crafted from thickened wire, this pot and pan organizer for cabinet offers exceptional stability, capable of holding most pots and pans without bending or warping.
      • Scratch-Free Pot ProtectionPots are more than just tools, but sources of yummy food and fond memories. MUDEELA pot pan rack uses cutting-edge 5.0 gum dipping, nesting your valued pots and protecting them from scratches. Every pot finds its loving home at the MUDEELA pot organizer rack for under the cabinet.
      • Versatile for Most Pots and PansThis pots and pans organizer under the cabinet keeps your pots, pans, lids, trays, cookie sheets, and more well organized and easy to reach. With this kitchen cabinet organizer, you no longer have to dig through cabinets or stacks of cookware to find what you need.

      Product description

      Great Solution For Keeping Your Pots/ Pans/ Lids Organized and Easy to Reach

      Worried about your kitchen being a mess and cant find your cookware?

      No Problem! Our pan organizer rack will help keep your pots, pans, lids, trays, plates, cookie sheets and cutting boards well organized and easy to reach

      Worried that the pot organizer can't support multiple large pots?

      No Problem! Our cabinet pot organizer rack has 8 tiers, allowing you to store 8 and more (stacked) pots and pans. Our pot and pan organizer is designed to be adjustable. You can adjust the position of each shelf to place different sizes of pots and pans on it.

      Worried about the pot rack organizer taking up a lot of space?

      No Problem! Our pot rack organizer is easy to assemble in 3 methods. Depending on the sizes of your pans, the rack can be adjusted according to meet your needs, giving you more flexibility in organizing your pots and pans. The compact design allows you to save a lot of space in your cabinets, pantries, and on your countertops

      If you have more heavy pots, we suggest you consider our new 8-tier adjustable heavy duty pan organizer rack for cabinet

      Minimum Cabinet Size Required: 24" x 18.5" x 9" (W x H x D)

      Greatly Helps to Organize Your Cookware - Your Kitchen Will No Longer Be A Mess!

      No longer a mess in your kitchen, cabinet, pantry and counter.Easy to reach your pots and pans

      Uses: Used in kitchen cabinets, pantries and on countertops

      3 DIY Methods Provide You with More Options

      Non-slip Silicone Layer

      Each layer of the pot rack has a silicone layer that will effectively stop the pots and pans from sliding and keep your pot pans stable in their place
